  "name": "Maw of Hungry Shadows",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Shadows swirl around this soot-black tome, swallowing up any light that touches them. A faint whispering emanates from the grimoire's pages when opened.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Your last action was to cast a spell prepared from this grimoire that has the shadow trait</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> Your shadow, and that of the tome, elongates and reaches hungrily for one foe within 30 feet, who must attempt a Fortitude save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.XgEqL1kFApUbl5Z2]{Blinded} for 1 round and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 1} as the shadows scrape across it.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is blinded for 1 minute and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 2} as the shadows seize it.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but the shadows also pull the creature into the tome, teleporting it to the Shadow Plane.</p>"
